### Global Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8181/api/v1/ia
@contentType = application/json

### Predict Customer Risk
GET {{baseUrl}}/predict-risk/101
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### Get Collection Strategy
GET {{baseUrl}}/collection-strategy/202
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### Generate Custom Reminder
GET {{baseUrl}}/generate-reminder/202
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### Weekly Executive Summary
GET {{baseUrl}}/weekly-summary
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
